<A>__{they have reached the outskirts of a village. beatrice turns off the main track and up a narrow path. hector follows her. soon she stops at a small house close to an orchard. the house sits in the mess of a run down farm yard, chickens and goats running here and there. beatrice opens the door of the house and goes inside. hector hesitates before following her.}
